Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是在朦朧之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}湧出的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時的我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無暇整理自己的心緒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我與學姐相識
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過一日而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼不能說出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說「為什麼」我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你怎麼可能當我戀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為你又比我小還戴眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這麼瘦弱而且戴著眼鏡又愛妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}咦 眼鏡出現了兩次？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還很色情 以自我為中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別再妄想了啊 我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前略 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不肖頑弟上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}令弟痴狂頑劣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}終猝死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不成器 歉之
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恥留於世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}起床了 海人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再不起來上學就要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吃早餐的時間也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「我今天休息」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}出什麼事了嗎？海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}身體沒有異狀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學 海人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「請不要管我 海人」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「我今天休息」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「請不要管我」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說我這樣放著他不管好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說回來為什麼口都不願意開要遞紙條來說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說這是什麼暗號…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是有趣啊 一夏你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我搞錯什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個啊 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是普通的偷懶逃學而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偷懶逃學？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是說霧島他有不想來學校的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比如不想讀書啊 不想看到某人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不想…看到？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天晚上 發生什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什…什麼都沒發生…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然有詭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}年輕真好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還記得昨天的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…大家在一起說電影的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後 乾杯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再然後玩撲克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到這裡都還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可這是之後就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不知什麼時候就睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}醒來頭就好疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}究竟是為什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喲 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你還記得昨天發生了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀…我也不太記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了對了 我上學的時候碰到檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她要我把這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不行不行不行！不能看！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說不能看就是不能看！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了啊 昨天的我到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 大家到位子上坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在開早會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}首先 由於霧島同學身體不適
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以今天缺席
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他感冒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天還挺精神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家也要好好注意身體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 現在點一下名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}相川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然是因為…知道了我的真實身份了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐你不是這個星球的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個人是外星人！超可怕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快來拯救地球啊 黑衣人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(765,658)}Men in Black
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}出自一部關於外星人的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}救命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不要當實驗體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}更不要解剖！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多麼…嚇人的事態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過究竟該如何跟海人說明好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是不是該和他坦白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可那時候海人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐她現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒！？被海人告白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊 昨天晚上突然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後你怎麼回答的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然是NO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人真是不知道自己有幾斤幾兩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也許他心裡很虛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還不如說是沒腦子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我腦子裡會冒出這麼不吉利的妄想來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幹嘛啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 你們不去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說去是去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去探望海人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}他現在不舒服著呢 過去只是添亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞不好他肚子正餓著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐在那裡 肯定好生伺候著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是一夏學姐肯定把海人照顧得服服貼貼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貼身扶腰喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}第一話出現過的neta 手取り足取り的誤用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來擦臉臉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:07:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡也得周到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從後面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}從前面來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美櫻 我想起來我有急事先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…柑菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去哪兒一目了然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗 這樣好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣…好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為…哲朗你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是個機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去是…去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 8mm攝像機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是學姐的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我就猜到可能會有這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像能拍到很「真實」的場景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不管什麼時候人都是會餓的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是叫什麼來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也要吃點什麼不？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快遞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷…谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個我…不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒說清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她也沒回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以別笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}臉很紅哦 身體還不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我稍微睡了一下就舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說謊不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實我今天是逃學了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為一些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你沒事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 這樣讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用道歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我已經放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是來看我的吧 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}站著說話不方便  進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 昨天才向我告白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天就帶另一個女生回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人真是肉食動物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}倒不如說是雜食
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…現在去哪逛逛不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你突然怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 可以是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我去換下衣服 你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要…要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很久沒去輕井澤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}順便為電影採外景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼 要出門嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學不是生病了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來 要上了哦 Snake
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}出自一款叫做合金裝備的潛入游戲 男主角的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就這樣不回去…去別的地方的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.27,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…姐姐拜託我了要照顧好海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人和谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐不是地球人啊 是外星人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}救命 快來拯救地球啊 黑衣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}聽得到嗎 理音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了 用連環讓我跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(648,660)}linkage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼毫無反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}人…人挺多的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}畢竟是七月的星期六嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要去哪裡採外景？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有仔細考慮過  就這麼逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就閒逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像在約會一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 人這麼多不方便攝影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種程度的準備是起碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這叫起碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}青春的光輝稍瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要留下它的倩影必須付出各種努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 我有點口渴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去買點果汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐也要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}跑到哪裡去了啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉…要你陪我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事啦 反正我也渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是大杯一點就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}霧島同學為什麼沒去學校呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那不是顯而易見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為貴月學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也許 這都請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是發生了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但這對柑菜來說卻是個好機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會被踢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}妨礙別人的戀情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}日語俗語妨礙別人戀情會被馬踢死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我有妨礙嗎  我可是在支持哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我懂得的 是妨礙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗會被踢的 被自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且…那大概
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}多謝你為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 那是美櫻你想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜對我而言只是一起長大的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦哦 真是不錯的景致
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找到適合的地方了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你啊 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒問我為什麼逃學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很在意…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你不想說的話 就不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是因為學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不是說有什麼特別的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}實際上 真的什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然啊 要突然和別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且是女孩子一起住 還是有不少得注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}貴月學姐畢竟是個美女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…身材也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是比我年長 而且又是外國人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能會有很多觀念上的差異
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想到這點…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}挺溫柔的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.83,0:15:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？檸檬學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在…做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃…怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太過追求畫面的美好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}忘記躲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你！在！拍！什！麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}青春無敵思春少女所做的稚嫩的告白…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你別說些莫名其妙的話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這可是偷拍哦！偷拍！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}赤裸裸的犯罪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說今天早上的照片是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}把那個樣子的我偷拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個樣子?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我和學姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟然跑了 學姐站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 跑到哪去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}找了你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呀 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都化了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼連美櫻你們都在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}額…這是檸檬學姐說要我們幫忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明是你自己要跟來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是檸檬學姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜 不是的…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們這些大壞蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才的聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊！對不…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學…學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有事…要和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:17:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊……！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.09,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼要跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼要追我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是有原因的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也有原因啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海他去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是不是已經回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是可惜啊 谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你笑什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼追到這…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你說原因…到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天 海人同學要說的那些話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是和我有關吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果被人知道的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會很糟糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}糟糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔…看情況也許…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可能會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看吧 肯定會！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不能繼續在海人家住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個地方也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實也沒必要非得搬出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然多少會有點尷尬…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒想到會讓你那麼為難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這件事就放在海人心裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不要跟大家說了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哈？怎麼可能說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很丟人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}丟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有那麼丟人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可是被拒絕了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯？被誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}提問
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐你覺得我昨天是想說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以說那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不可告人的秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有這樣的秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}提問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.01,0:20:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天海人是想說什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可告人的秘密是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}耍賴…先回答我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.52,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果學姐說的話我也說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的不知道嗎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天一天都還沒吃過東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們都沒提到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只說了一些不痛不癢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比如興趣…喜歡的食物什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}知道了我們還僅僅是這樣的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總感覺心裡卻變得輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}擅自拍攝可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正以後也要拍很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好…朝這邊看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗨 海人同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}除了昨天的事 我還有事要問
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你究竟是被誰拒絕了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是誰是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有被誰拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…有沒有喜歡的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是谷川同學吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天也在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…是北原同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}都說了不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}難不成是我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開…玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}A君向B醬告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}Amy醬向B太君…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}C醬有危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底誰是誰阿 搞不清了

